Jack McDonald (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_McDonald_(actor) 0 Jack McDonald (September 17, 1880 – 1962) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 71 films between 1912 and 1930. He was born in San Francisco, California. Jack_McDonald ( September_17 , 1880 – 1962 ) was an_American_actor of the_silent_era . He appeared in 71_films between 1912_and_1930 . He was_born in San_Francisco , California .
